import * as React from "react";
import { getOverrideProps } from "@aws-amplify/ui-react/internal";
import { Button, Text, View } from "@aws-amplify/ui-react";
export default function FormularioLogin(props) {
  const { login, overrides, ...rest } = props;
  return (
    <View
      width="500px"
      height="557.14px"
      display="block"
      gap="unset"
      alignItems="unset"
      justifyContent="unset"
      position="relative"
      padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
      {...getOverrideProps(overrides, "FormularioLogin")}
      {...rest}
    >
      <Text
        fontFamily="Inter"
        fontSize="20px"
        fontWeight="400"
        color="rgba(0,44,133,1)"
        lineHeight="30px"
        textAlign="left"

        justifyContent="unset"
        width="436px"
        height="67px"
        gap="unset"
        alignItems="unset"
        position="absolute"
        top="17.57%"
        bottom="70.41%"
        left="6.2%"
        right="6.6%"
        padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
        whiteSpace="pre-wrap"
        children="Ingresa tu usuario y contraseña para iniciar sesión"
        {...getOverrideProps(
          overrides,
          "Ingresa tu usuario y contrase\u00F1a para iniciar sesi\u00F3n"
        )}
      ></Text>
      <Button
        width="324px"
        height="33px"
        justifyContent="flex-start"
        position="absolute"
        top="92.8%"

        size="small"
        isDisabled={false}
        variation="link"

      ></Button>
      <Text

        fontSize="20px"

        textAlign="left"
        display="block"
        direction="column"
        justifyContent="unset"
        width="436px"
        height="67px"
        gap="unset"
        alignItems="unset"
        position="absolute"
        top="87.97%"
        bottom="0%"
        left="6.4%"
        right="6.4%"
        padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
        whiteSpace="pre-wrap"
        children="Recuerda que si aún no tienes una cuenta puedes "
        {...getOverrideProps(
          overrides,
          "Recuerda que si a\u00FAn no tienes una cuenta puedes"
        )}
      ></Text>
      <Text
        fontFamily="Inter"
        fontSize="32px"
        fontWeight="500"
        color="rgba(0,44,133,1)"
        lineHeight="40px"
        textAlign="left"
        display="block"
        direction="column"
        justifyContent="unset"
        width="436px"
        height="67px"
        gap="unset"
        alignItems="unset"
        position="absolute"
        top="0.18%"
        bottom="87.79%"
        left="6.3%"
        right="6.5%"
        padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
        whiteSpace="pre-wrap"
        children="Hola, nos da mucho gusto que estés aquí"
        {...getOverrideProps(
          overrides,
          "Hola, nos da mucho gusto que est\u00E9s aqu\u00ED"
        )}
      ></Text>
      <View
        padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
        width="492px"
        height="290px"
        display="block"
        gap="unset"
        alignItems="unset"
        justifyContent="unset"
        position="absolute"
        top="176px"
        left="4px"
        children={login}
        {...getOverrideProps(overrides, "Formulario")}
      ></View>
    </View>
  );
}
